metadata.othernotes:
General Info:

-She ran away from her family in pursuit of adventure and to escape her noble lifestyle. Her father was worried at first but trusts her current party will take care of her and keep her from getting too carried away.

-She can't hit anything with her sword as she put almost everything into defensive stats.

-Because she put everything into defensive stats, she is incredibly tough and resilient, as well as incredibly strong due to keeping herself in physical shape. She has on one or two occasions been hit by one of Megumin's explosions and managed to walk away alive.

-While she is a masochist, she prefers actually being outdone by others and usually doesn't purposefully lose... Usually.

-She absolutely despises being called by her real name, as that is the one thing that embarrasses her in a way she doesn't enjoy. I won't put her real name here, but if you manage to figure it out, good job. This might require the assistance of one of her party members however as she is pretty tight-lipped about it.

-Darkness actually usually doesn't go absolutely crazy with her fantasies to the point where she loses herself in desire or anything, but that's also because her kinks combined with her off putting personality when those kinks are expressed make most people backpedal away from the situation. Since this game will be putting her in a much more erotic situation for an extended period of time, the results may differ.

-Surprisingly, Darkness is actually a worshipper of a goddess. She is the goddess of luck and the most popular goddess in Belzerg (her home region). The goddess's name is Eris.

-While darkness has pretty intense fantasies sometimes, she also has a sense of the difference between reality and fantasy, and when put in a position that would actually suck such as family attempting to marry her away to someone she doesn't like, she actually hates it. She won't actually put herself in a situation that makes her life more miserable.


Writing Ideas:

If you don't feel like your character plays well with her perverted personality, don't be afraid to engage her more in casual conversation. It might be harder for her to respond normally in the later stages, but I generally try to keep stages 0-4 wide open for casual conversation. (You can still do casual conversation in the other stages, she just may be a bit more in a perverted mindset with her answers).

Teasing her then backpedaling when you realize what you just got yourself into with her is always fun.

Don't be afraid to question/inquire her on/about her kinks and masochism. You might learn an interesting tidbit about her potentially depending on how it goes.
